[{"url_token": "liu-xia-qing-feng-48", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "842470685", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "842470685", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "最后悔的事：叫亲戚装修", "like_count": 147, "author_name": "乘风", "author_id": "e550e6d1dce838b1a45adbd1857d70cd", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "chang-sha-zhuang-xiu-xian-sheng", "headline": "装修施工现场负责人", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "842497462", "reply_comment_id": "842470685", "reply_root_comment_id": "842470685", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我不这样认为。<br><br>当然啦，有两个原因是会后悔的：1.你的亲戚本身的专业技术欠缺；2.你没有让你亲戚赚应有的利润。有这两个原因，是不是亲戚都会后悔的。<br><br>自己有亲戚朋友是做装修的，只要他足够专业，放心去找吧。钱给谁不是赚呢，肥水不流外人田呢。出了问题至少还能找到人。而我们选择业主（浅交的朋友亲戚关系），如果知道对方难打交道或者过于小气，我们一般会说忙不过来。<br><br>所以，您自己体会，自己选择吧。", "like_count": 16, "author_name": "长沙装修小队长", "author_id": "2fb98698c25fe5d7e47989ac77706663", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "chen-hong-song-gao-da", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "1822005960", "reply_comment_id": "842470685", "reply_root_comment_id": "842470685", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "不能找亲戚，不是钱的事情，而是容易闹矛盾，不满意的时候沟通反而更困难，说也不好说", "like_count": 17, "author_name": "陈红松(高达)", "author_id": "977bd881db8284ed1da7db863de2a405", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "liu-xia-qing-feng-48", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "983323756", "reply_comment_id": "979864786", "reply_root_comment_id": "842470685", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "一两个月可以完工的事，我舅舅硬是给我拖了两年，到现在还没完工，而且质量差的要命，敷衍了事搞了一下。最后悔的是我一早就把一大部分钱给了他，买了石灰水泥瓷片沙子之类的硬是给我堆到不能用，换做是别人，早上门去打他了。", "like_count": 5, "author_name": "乘风", "author_id": "e550e6d1dce838b1a45adbd1857d70cd", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "xiao-zu-zong-zhao-zhao", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4693165607", "reply_c