-xian-sheng", "headline": "装修施工现场负责人", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10097695648", "reply_comment_id": "982592998", "reply_root_comment_id": "842470685", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "姐夫同学，姐姐同学，哥哥同学，同你的关系，都不一样的。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "长沙装修小队长", "author_id": "2fb98698c25fe5d7e47989ac77706663", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "bu-suan-41", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4647589531", "reply_comment_id": "4363885339", "reply_root_comment_id": "842470685", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "应有的利润，意思就是低于市场价，总价少了，你说利润从哪里找？不是换材料，就是降低做工的积极性。背了亲戚的名，哪个施工队好意思报市场价？找亲戚的人，有几个大方到只要求质量不图便宜？", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "不酸", "author_id": "aebb5db9121db12961a672a371ab67f9", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "liu-xia-qing-feng-48", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "3709696428", "reply_comment_id": "3690525802", "reply_root_comment_id": "842470685", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "反正考察清楚摸清底细找外边人就对了[大笑]白纸黑字全写清楚，出了问题该怎么样怎么样，省心", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "乘风", "author_id": "e550e6d1dce838b1a45adbd1857d70cd", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "liu-xia-qing-feng-48", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "2808946461", "reply_comment_id": "2792566140", "reply_root_comment_id": "842470685", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "大把施工队，看看周围邻居朋友找的什么装修公司，对比一下再选择就行", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "乘风", "author_id": "e550e6d1dce838b1a45adbd1857d70cd", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "ling-shang-kong-jue", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "2792566140", "reply_comment_id": "842470685", "reply_root_comment_id": "842470685", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "没时间，找谁呀。。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "零觞空绝", "author_id": "de1bf41cca8ad2ec854fe3adff1cefb6", "auth